{"tid":2019524,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"有無見過黑人支持種族歧視黑人？","createTime":"2020-05-16T10:40:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T16:58:42.000Z","uid":10779,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3088503d6e97abdb19254148e9591c14db4d5942","tid":2019524,"uid":10779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T10:40:16.000Z","msg":"從來無人會支持其他人種族歧視自己民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n可能對好多外國人嚟講 香港人=中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但如果我地大規模咁支持佢哋歧視中國人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁樣會唔會令佢哋諗<br />\n吓？邊有人支持我哋racist佢哋架？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通佢哋唔係中國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n從而帶出 #HongKongISNOTChina？<br />\n<br />\n就好似今次咁<br />\n有餐廳歧視中國人唔俾佢哋幫襯<br />\n連米芝連都要除佢名<br />\n但香港人竟然大力支持？<br />\n班外國人會點諗呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/citFV1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcitFV1Q.jpg&h=2119767d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但同時都有可能得罪反racist 嘅左膠 <br />\n大家點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"474a36586a944630316b1b68f4deef348b2d1da0","tid":2019524,"uid":10779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T10:40:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9cb853bd31ee7ac0d7ef9a2001c1abf20c7071","tid":2019524,"uid":10779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T10:41:13.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78acf0ddae8104afd68d080810cb1001e3761117","tid":2019524,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T10:46:11.000Z","msg":"豬仔會唔會令到佢佢地以為矮化佢地?  雖然我地明姐"},{"pid":"5d8883a0c3930ac92eb6ccb11b0a4e3867dcc188","tid":2019524,"uid":10779,"l