tent%3Dlink_post&d=IqGrl%2FmL2I6%2Fp6gKwmVM%2BQsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=bb3bb681\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200516%2F6TXMQZE6KDKK6NN7RQEGNPDQRA%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=a400ff14\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200516/6TXMQZE6KDKK6NN7RQEGNPDQRA/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a><br />\n#武漢肺炎<br />\n【德餐廳重開「不歡迎中國人」遭搣星 名廚解釋︰說給獨裁者聽的】<br />\n<br />\n德國一間米芝蓮一星餐廳的名廚布爾蓋伊日前宣佈重新營業後「不歡迎中國人」，被批評種族歧視，當地華人發起抵制。<br />\n<br />\n雖然布爾蓋伊澄清無意針對華人，這番說話只是批評中國「獨裁者」和「強權」，但無法平息風波。米芝蓮昨晚宣佈，將這家餐廳從推介榜單除名，並強烈譴責其言論。"},{"pid":"0c8b541ddfeff269587c7f6a8c9ca274bfb65d8e","tid":2019524,"uid":10779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T11:55:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"644d20debe9e14b419db29da4586543aba05d1ff","tid":2019524,"uid":10779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:06:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c9eca3f216ae9b9ab1a7636403ce0937dbf801","tid":2019524,"uid":37869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:45:03.000Z","msg":"我覺得歧視問題喺西方好似玩火咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好唔好掂呢個問題"},{"pid":"5703b392faa33a726602e11b943fbe3493fb5202","tid":2019524,"uid":10779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1c9eca3f216ae9b9ab1a7636403ce0937dbf801","tid":2019524,"uid":37869,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T12:45:03.000Z","msg":"我覺得歧視問題喺西方好似玩火咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好唔好掂呢個問題"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-16T13:16:12.000Z","msg":"如果轉個講法話支持呢個廚師反中共反獨裁者呢？"},{"pid":"79c08d4478401974b600263947cee1ba7100aac5","tid":2019524,"uid":8729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,